- Here is the contract of Paul:
I am honored to join the space program of The Union and I am willing to risk my life to explore space. Therefore, I renounce every right I have to sue The Union in the event of my death.
Signed: Astronaut Paul
- And here is the declaration of Astronaut Paul, ready to send to the press:
I am thrilled that I have been chosen in the space program of The Union. I will make The Union and my family proud by being a good astronaut, dedicated to the exploration of space. Cheers and see you on Venus !
Signed: Astronaut Paul

Number of Helmets: 8 - Number of Suits: 21

- Here is the contract of Laura:
